{
    "title": "Sandra",
    "artist": "Gilberto Gil",
    "composer": "Gilberto Gil",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Solo] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> \n\n\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Maria Aparecida, porque apareceu na vida</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Maria Sebastiana, porque Deus fez tão bonita</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Maria de Lourdes</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Porque me pediu uma canção pra ela</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Carmensita, porque ela sussurrou seja \"bem-vindo\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No meu ouvido</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na primeira noite quando nós chegamos no hospício</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E Lair, Lair</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Porque quis me ver e foi lá no hospício</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Salete fez chafé, que é um chá de café que eu gosto</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E naquela semana tomar chafé foi um vício</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Andréia na estréia</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No segundo dia, meus laços de fita</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Cintia, porque, embora choque, rosa é cor bonita</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E Ana, porque parece uma cigana da ilha</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>               \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dulcina, porque</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É santa, é uma santa e me beijou na boca</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>    \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Azul, porque azul é cor, e cor é fé, menina</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu sou tão inseguro porque o muro é muito alto</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E pra dar o salto</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me amarro na torre no alto da montanha</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Amarradão na torre dá pra ir pro mundo inteiro</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E onde quer que eu vá no mundo, vejo a minha torre</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>             \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É só balançar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que a corda me leva de volta pra ela</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Oh, Sandra!</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Amarradão na torre dá pra ir pro mundo inteiro</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>                                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(4)\">D7(4)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E onde quer que eu vá no mundo, vejo a minha torre</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>             \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É só balançar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que a corda me leva de volta pra ela</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Maria de Lourdes</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Porque me pediu uma canção pra ela</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>               \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dulcina, porque</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É santa, é uma santa e me beijou na boca</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Andréia na estréia</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No segundo dia, meus laços de fita</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>             \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É só balançar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que a corda me leva de volta pra ela</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Oh, Sandra!</span>\n",
